v1.3.1
======
Added a fix to ensure that only desktop browser windows are maximised.  Trying to maximse a device browser is currently unsupported.

v1.3
======
Added ability to run tests on iOS and Android devices on Sauce Labs.  Simply define BROWSER to be "iphone", "ipad" or "android" along with a valid version number and you're good to go!

v1.2.8
======
Changes made to SelectBox.java:
  Fixed and renamed getAllOptions method to getOptions.
  Added a new method called getSelectedOptions.
